<th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Notable ideas</th>
<td class="infobox-data">
<a href="/wiki/Arab_Winter" title="Arab Winter">Arab Winter</a><br>The End of the <a href="/wiki/End_of_history" title="End of history">End of History</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>1<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
